    {
      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "County Superintendent of Schools\nfrom his state examination papers.\nThere were 1874 examinations, 81 of\nwhich received certificates. There\nwere II first grade, Al second grade\nand 80 third grade.\n\n\nThe tests in arithmetic and school\nlaw were unusually difficult this year.\nMany of the teachers making excel\nlent showings in all other branches\nfailed in those subjects."
